        <div class="well">
          <h4>
            Tips
          </h4>
          <p>
            Use Promoted Tweets in search and timelines to own the conversation around breaking news. Optimize keywords in real time to maximize the reach of your message. 
          </p>
          <p>
            <a href="https://twitter.com/AFER" target="_blank" class="btn">Check out @AFER →</a>
          </p>
